extends ../main

block content

  h1(style="margin-bottom: 30px") Help out #{ user.profile.name }

  p Hey #{ recipient },

  p #{ user.profile.name } has invited you to help out with an instance of Ideaboard which they help manage.

  p If you already have an account registered with the same email just click the following link to authenticate and accept the invitation.

  <a style="color: #0B9BD0" href="http://localhost:8080/auth">Accept invitation</a>

  p If not then ask them to invite you via your other email address or alternatively create a new account with this email.
  
  <a style="color: #0B9BD0" href="http://localhost:8080/auth">Create account</a>